    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional 2006 Mitsubishi Lancer Evolution IX MR, preserved in showroom condition. This specimen features the revered 4G63 inline-four power plant, utilizing MIVEC variable valve timing and a twin-scroll TD05HR turbocharger for optimized volumetric efficiency. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed close-ratio manual transmission and the sophisticated Super Active Yaw Control (S-AYC) system, ensuring neutral handling under high lateral G-loads. The chassis remains factory-stiff, supported by MR-specific Bilstein monotube dampers that provide impeccable damping rates and rebound control. Free of any oxidation or mechanical lash, this unmodified unit represents the pinnacle of Japanese homologation engineering. A true turn-key investment for the serious collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
