    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presented in museum-quality condition, this vehicle is a true time capsule for the discerning collector. The exterior paint retains its deep, glass-like factory luster, completely free of swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings, having been stored in a climate-controlled environment under a soft cover. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine, showroom state; the premium leather upholstery shows zero bolster wear, and the original 'new car' scent remains. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the intricate ambient lighting and dual-zone climate control, functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by master technicians. We have a complete, chronological binder of service records documenting every fluid flush and preventative measure taken. The tires are recently replaced high-performance rubber, the brakes are sharp, and the transmission shifts with seamless, factory-spec precision. This is a meticulously preserved investment-grade vehicle that offers a driving experience indistinguishable from a brand-new model.",
